## 🎨 Design System & UI Components

### shadcn/ui Component Strategy
**Essential Components for HomelabARR v2.0**:
- **data-table**: Docker container management (sorting, filtering, pagination, actions)
- **card**: Dashboard widgets (system stats, storage, monitoring)
- **chart**: CPU/RAM/Network graphs using Chart.js integration
- **progress**: Storage usage bars with real-time updates
- **badge**: Status indicators (running/stopped/update available)
- **dialog**: App installation modals with multi-step wizards
- **sidebar**: Navigation menu (Unraid-style collapsed/expanded)
- **toast/sonner**: Success/error notifications with persistence
- **dropdown-menu**: Container actions (start/stop/restart/logs)
- **command**: Quick command palette (Spotlight-style search)

