#### Story Point Estimation (Time-Based System)
**CRITICAL**: This violates Scrum rules by equating time to story points, but provides concrete development metrics.

- **0.25 SP = 2 hours** of actual heads-down coding time (not meetings/docs)
- **0.5 SP = 4 hours** of focused development work
- **1 SP = 8 hours** (full day of coding)
- **2 SP = 16 hours** (2 full coding days)
- **3 SP = 24 hours** (3 days maximum)
- **5 SP = 40 hours** (full week of development)
- **8 SP = 64 hours** (should be broken down)

